  "texts": [
    "Models with robust detection capabilities and strong generalization performance are required to overcome the great challenge of accurately detecting and localizing complex defects.",
    "This paper performs a comprehensive and reliable performance evaluation of the improved model using two defect datasets collected from real-world scenarios, and the study results provide insights into the model's performance in practical applications.",
    "The primary contributions of this paper are summarized as follows:",
    "• The MSF strategy is proposed to enhance the faulty features' representation capacity.",
    "It efficiently increases image resolution while acquiring more robust semantic information by combining the benefits of feature maps of various scales."
